      "id": "sybil_6_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\ude97 I\u2019m selling my absolute gem of a car, and it\u2019s looking for a great new home! It\u2019s been super reliable and is in really wonderful shape\u2014honestly, it drives like a dream and has been so well-loved over the years. Whether you're commuting to work or heading out on a weekend road trip, this ride is ready to go! It\u2019s clean, comfy, and has tons of life left in it. I\u2019d love for you to come by, take it for a spin, and see for yourself how great it is! \u2728",
