    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "Up for sale is a meticulously maintained vehicle that strikes the perfect balance between luxury and utility. The exterior features a deep metallic finish that still catches the light beautifully; while the body is straight, a close inspection will reveal a few minor stone chips on the front hood and a small scuff on the rear passenger-side bumper consistent with careful daily use. Inside, the cabin remains a sanctuary. The premium leather seats are supple, showing only light natural creasing on the driver\u2019s side bolster, and the carpets have been protected by all-weather mats since day one. All electronic components\u2014including the high-resolution infotainment screen, dual-zone climate control, and heated seating\u2014function exactly as intended. Mechanically, this car is turn-key ready. It has a documented history of synthetic oil changes every 5,000 miles, and the transmission shifts smoothly under all driving conditions. The tires have approximately 70% tread remaining, and the brake system was recently inspected with plenty of pad life left. There are no leaks, no odd noises, and no dashboard warning lights. This is a reliable, honest car that has been treated with respect and is ready for its next owner.",
      "price": 31500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
